#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:41
msgid "1. Acceptance of Terms"
msgstr "1. Aceptación de los Términos"

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:43
msgid ""
"By accessing or using PredictStamp, you agree to these Terms and Conditions."
" If you do not agree, do not use the platform."
msgstr ""
"Al acceder o usar PredictStamp, aceptas estos Términos y Condiciones. Si no "
"estás de acuerdo, no uses la plataforma."

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:48
msgid "2. The Service"
msgstr "2. El Servicio"

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:50
msgid ""
"PredictStamp lets users browse prediction-market-related topics, publish "
"comments, create formal forecasts, participate in social challenges, and "
"build public reputation and popularity records."
msgstr ""
"PredictStamp permite explorar temas de mercados de predicción, publicar "
"comentarios, crear pronósticos formales, participar en desafíos sociales y "
"construir historial público de reputación y popularidad."

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:55
msgid "3. No Financial Activity"
msgstr "3. Sin actividad financiera"

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:57
msgid ""
"PredictStamp is not a betting, gambling, trading, brokerage, exchange, "
"custody, wallet, investment advisory, or financial services platform. You "
"cannot deposit funds, place wagers, trade contracts, withdraw funds, or "
"receive payouts through PredictStamp."
msgstr ""
"PredictStamp no es una plataforma de apuestas, juego, trading, corretaje, "
"bolsa, custodia, billetera, asesoría de inversión ni servicios financieros. "
"No puedes depositar fondos, apostar, operar contratos, retirar fondos ni "
"recibir pagos a través de PredictStamp."

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:62
msgid "4. User Content and Conduct"
msgstr "4. Contenido y conducta del usuario"

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:64
msgid ""
"You are responsible for the content you post, including comments, forecasts,"
" reasoning, votes, and profile information. Do not post illegal, misleading,"
" abusive, infringing, spam, or malicious content. We may remove content or "
"restrict accounts that violate these Terms or harm the platform."
msgstr ""
"Eres responsable del contenido que publicas, incluidos comentarios, "
"pronósticos, razonamiento, votos e información de perfil. No publiques "
"contenido ilegal, engañoso, abusivo, infractor, spam o malicioso. Podemos "
"eliminar contenido o restringir cuentas que violen estos Términos o dañen la"
" plataforma."

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:69
msgid "5. Reputation and Popularity"
msgstr "5. Reputación y popularidad"

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:71
msgid ""
"Reputation and popularity scores are platform-specific social metrics. They "
"are not money, securities, tokens, credits, rewards, or transferable "
"property, and they have no cash value."
msgstr ""
"Las puntuaciones de reputación y popularidad son métricas sociales de la "
"plataforma. No son dinero, valores, tokens, créditos, recompensas ni "
"propiedad transferible, y no tienen valor en efectivo."

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:76
msgid "6. Third-Party Data"
msgstr "6. Datos de terceros"

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:78
msgid ""
"PredictStamp may display or reference third-party market data, links, "
"outcomes, and metadata. Third-party data may be delayed, incomplete, "
"inaccurate, or unavailable. PredictStamp is not responsible for third-party "
"services or content."
msgstr ""
"PredictStamp puede mostrar o referenciar datos, enlaces, resultados y "
"metadatos de mercados de terceros. Esos datos pueden estar retrasados, "
"incompletos, inexactos o no disponibles. PredictStamp no es responsable de "
"servicios o contenido de terceros."

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:83
msgid "7. No Advice"
msgstr "7. Sin asesoramiento"

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:85
msgid ""
"Content on PredictStamp is for informational and social discussion purposes "
"only. It is not financial, investment, legal, tax, or professional advice."
msgstr ""
"El contenido en PredictStamp es solo para información y debate social. No es"
" asesoramiento financiero, de inversión, legal, fiscal ni profesional."

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:90
msgid "8. Accounts and Availability"
msgstr "8. Cuentas y disponibilidad"

#: templates/dashboard/terms.html:92
msgid ""
"You are responsible for maintaining account security. We may update, "
"suspend, limit, or discontinue any part of the platform at any time, "
"including features, rankings, scoring formulas, and content availability."
msgstr ""
"Eres responsable de la seguridad de tu cuenta. Podemos actualizar, "
"suspender, limitar o discontinuar cualquier parte de la plataforma en "
"cualquier momento, incluidas funciones, rankings, fórmulas de puntuación y "
"disponibilidad de contenido."

