#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:125
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "Arquitectura"

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:126
msgid "One batch per day"
msgstr "Un batch por día"

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:128
msgid ""
"We do not spam the chain with every click. Once every 24 hours, PredictStamp"
" bundles every realized position into a Merkle tree and anchors the root on "
"Base."
msgstr ""
"No spameamos la cadena con cada clic. Una vez cada 24 horas, PredictStamp "
"agrupa cada posición realizada en un árbol Merkle y ancla la raíz en Base."

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:135
msgid "You act"
msgstr "Actuás"

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:136
msgid ""
"Enter a market, exit early, or hold to resolution. Reputation changes only "
"when the position closes."
msgstr ""
"Entrás a un mercado, salís antes o mantenés hasta la resolución. La "
"reputación cambia solo cuando se cierra la posición."

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:140
msgid "We sign"
msgstr "Firmamos"

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:141
msgid ""
"Each event gets an off-chain attestation instantly — no wallet required from"
" you."
msgstr ""
"Cada evento recibe una attestation off-chain al instante — no necesitás "
"wallet."

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:145
msgid "We batch"
msgstr "Agrupamos"

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:146
msgid ""
"Leaves = entry + close + points. Hashed into a Merkle root for the rolling "
"24h window."
msgstr ""
"Hojas = entrada + cierre + puntos. Hasheadas en una raíz Merkle para la "
"ventana móvil de 24 h."

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:150
msgid "Base anchors"
msgstr "Base ancla"

#: templates/integrations/proof_index.html:151
msgid ""
"One transaction commits the root. Anyone verifies a row with a Merkle proof "
"— pennies per day."
msgstr ""
